OPPORTUNITY - COMPETITIVE RENTS & INCENTIVES 

Level 11 | 930sqm - Full floor fitout with reception, boardroom, 4 meeting rooms, 16 offices, breakout, comms, utility and potential 64 workstations (subject to furniture procurement). Fantastic river views. 


BUILDING 

40 The Esplanade is a modern 12 level boutique office tower in an outstanding location offering floor plates of exceptional flexibility and natural light due to its corner location. The building has been upgraded in recent years including the ground floor lobby including alfresco area, coffee hub, meeting areas, premium end of trip facilities with towel service, bathrooms and on-floor foyers. 

Other technical upgrades include lifts; mechanical services; fire control, security and EWIS systems. 

The building is perfectly positioned to take full advantage of the vibrancy of Elizabeth Quay and its growing momentum as the desired location for investors, businesses, employees, and tourists. With a brilliant and practical design, the architecture and workmanship has enabled the building to maximise the benefits of natural light and the inspiring panoramic views from every level.

LOCATION 

Positioned at the corner of William Street and The Esplanade diagonally opposite the Elizabeth Quay transport hub with freeway access from both North and South.

OUTGOINGS

Estimated at $165/sqm for the 2021/22 financial year.


CAR PARKING

Car parking available @ $650 pcm per bay. Current ratio of 1 bay per 170sqm. Public car parking available onsite for tenant use. 


NABERS

4.5-STAR NABERS Energy rating.

MANAGEMENT 

Onsite property and asset management.

BUILDING UPGRADES

- Upgrade and activation of the ground floor lobby (2018)
- Creation of outdoor courtyard and alfresco area (2018)
- Premium end of trip facilities (2019)
